":1},{"id":"recV2VLKz20IKBZ1N","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Aroer","slug":"aroer_93","score":1},{"id":"rec5pDuWtEaOK7ehk","type":"event","group":"event","label":"Prophecies of Jeremiah","slug":"event-234","score":47}],"links":[{"source":"reczsPBvGRhD29FNl","target":"rec3jLxfw7hvvvw7J","label":"part of"},{"source":"reczsPBvGRhD29FNl","target":"rec3qiPi8JN2h86Mj","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczsPBvGRhD29FNl","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczsPBvGRhD29FNl","target":"recCWY7OHg1GzDtTq","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczsPBvGRhD29FNl","target":"recyWfFMHv6ZLJkxq","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczsPBvGRhD29FNl","target":"recUn6eVJDoG4xI0j","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczsPBvGRhD29FNl","target":"recabsaJkxxtgdUSt","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczsPBvGRhD29FNl","target":"recoMMN7G2f7qaQuj","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczsPBvGRhD29FNl","target":"recMNg0pz95anDnCU","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczsPBvGRhD29FNl","target":"receKKjJVBBYJWFPx","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczsPBvGRhD29FNl","target":"rechszjphdueUPvPi","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczsPBvGRhD29FNl","target":"recQCdxZzUuCjYJVC","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczsPBvGRhD29FNl","target":"rec6SbCLgE1pnIMgt","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczsPBvGRhD29FNl","target":"recJK76HLZSOzxTWW","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczsPBvGRhD29FNl","target":"recV2VLKz20IKBZ1N","label":"mentions"},{"source":"reczsPBvGRhD29FNl","target":"rec5pDuWtEaOK7ehk","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"reccwdnnd4ajxIyHI","ref":"Jer.48.1","text":"Against Moab thus saith the LORD of hosts, the God of Israel; Woe unto Nebo! for it is spoiled: Kiriathaim is confounded and taken: Misgab is confounded and dismayed.","year":-584},{"id":"recWJrt4UhBmyvUF8","ref":"Jer.48.2","text":"There shall be no more praise of Moab: in Heshbon they have devised evil against it; come, and let us cut it off from being a nation. Also thou shalt be cut down, O Madmen; the sword shall pursue thee.","year":-584},{"id":"recGcdiasWRanPltK","ref":"Jer.48.3","text":"A voice of crying shall be from Horonaim, spoiling and great destruction.","year":-584},{"id":"recBHFGDnD2KBeB38","ref":"Jer.48.4","text":"Moab is destroyed; her little ones have caused a cry to be heard.","year":-584},{"id":"recjKGSOVw7kWqOKR","ref":"Jer.48.5","text":"For in the going up of Luhith continual weeping shall go up; for in the going down of Horonaim the enemies have heard a cry of destruction.","year":-584},{"id":"recePFXWT29qz327O","ref":"Jer.48.6","text":"Flee, save your lives, and be like the heath in the wilderness.","year":-584},{"id":"recIcjnoizxhXjt33","ref":"Jer.48.7","text":"For because thou hast trusted in thy works and in thy treasures, thou shalt also be taken: and Chemosh shall go forth into captivity with his priests and his princes together.","year":-584},{"id":"recYzNjAwu3imjl5O","ref":"Jer.48.8","text":"And the spoiler shall come upon every city, and no city shall escape: the valley also shall perish, and the plain shall be destroyed, as the LORD hath spoken.","year":-584}]}
